textBeforeTable: Call us on FREEPHONE 0800 298 0 4980800 298 0 498  to book or to ask any questions. Our upcoming Awaydays are listed below, we do hope you will find something to enjoy!  Click on the links to find out more information. Book and Pay for your day trip 2 or more weeks in advance of departure and receive 10% off the Coach Fare, must be booked directly through Bakers.  Can not be used in conjunction with any other offer, Theatre Tickets, Shows, Buckingham Palace, Coronation Street and Madness Trip. Early Bird Offer...   Unfortunately we are not able to offer Cheshire pick ups (except Congleton) throughout the Winter months. Awaydays from Mid Cheshire   We offer an excellent array of Awaydays throughout the year.  With pick up points in Stoke on Trent and Congleton or the option leave your car at our depot while you travel on your day trip by Coach it couldn't be easier to travel with us!  For a full list of our Awayday pick up points please see the bottom of this page.
